  "description": "<p>There may be ways other than a fight to the death to fulfill your monster hunting vow. If you get a hit on the End the Fight move and are unsure as to the outcome, you may roll percentile dice (2d10) on the following table. Note that for a strong hit on your End the Fight, you only use the tens digit of the percentile dice. On a weak hit, you use both the tens and the ones digit separately.</p>",
